  "title": "THERAPY ASSISTANT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist therapists in conducting therapy sessions</p></li><li><p>Prepare and clean therapy rooms and equipment</p></li><li><p>Guide patients during exercises as instructed by therapists</p></li><li><p>Monitor patients’ condition and report progress or concerns</p></li><li><p>Support daily administrative and record-keeping tasks</p></li><li><p>Ensure a safe, clean, and comfortable therapy environment</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>No experience required; training will be provided</p></li><li><p>Caring, patient, and responsible attitude</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills</p></li><li><p>Willingness to learn and follow instructions</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and able to assist patients</p></li><li><p>Relevant healthcare or therapy experience is an advantage</p></li></ul>",
